<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٧٩٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6245">أَبُو إِيَاسٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">«لَا عَيْشَ إِلَّا عَيْشُ الْآخِرَةِ … فَأَصْلِحِ الْأَنْصَارَ وَالْمُهَاجِرَةَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَعَنْ قَتَادَةَ، عَنْ أَنَسٍ، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> مِثْلَهُ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> فَاغْفِرْ لِلْأَنْصَارِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>